des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your Eva-Dry products after connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our Eva-Dry app in app market then register an account;
(2) Configure our devices in our Eva-Dry app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3) Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4) Search Eva-Dry skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5) Enable Eva-Dry skill, and you'll be navigated to the Eva-Dry login page;
(6) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7) Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the dehumidifier.”
“Alexa, turn off the dehumidifier.”
“Alexa, set the dehumidifier humidity Control to 40%.”
“Alexa, set the dehumidifier fan speed to low.”
“Alexa, set the dehumidifier fan speed to high.”
“Alexa, set the dehumidifier shut down timer to 4h.”
“Alexa, cancel the dehumidifier shut down timer.”
"Alexa, turn on the dehumidifier tank light"
"Alexa, turn off the dehumidifier tank light."
